vocabulary bundle <http://example.com/LeaderOntology/vocabulary/bundle#> as ^bundle {
	
	includes <http://example.com/LeaderOntology/vocabulary/activities#>
	includes <http://example.com/LeaderOntology/vocabulary/base#> 
	includes <http://example.com/LeaderOntology/vocabulary/competencies#>
	includes <http://example.com/LeaderOntology/vocabulary/impacts#>  
	includes <http://example.com/LeaderOntology/vocabulary/decisionProcess#>
	includes <http://example.com/LeaderOntology/vocabulary/leadershipStyles#> 
	includes <http://example.com/LeaderOntology/vocabulary/strategies#> 
	includes <http://example.com/LeaderOntology/vocabulary/tools#>  
}